    "15786612": {
      "title": "The resolution property for schemes and stacks",
      "abstract": "We prove the equivalence of two fundamental properties of algebraic stacks: being a quotient stack in a strong sense, and the resolution property, which says that every coherent sheaf is a quotient of some vector bundle. Moreover, we prove these properties in the important special case of orbifolds whose associated algebraic space is a scheme. (Mathematics Subject Classification: Primary 14A20, Secondary 14L30.)"
